# Copy to .env and fill in. NEVER commit .env — and keep real values out of
# this file too; it is committed and must only ever contain placeholders.
#
# Use Alpaca PAPER keys (dashboard: paper account -> API keys). The code never
# reads a base-URL variable: every client is constructed paper=True against
# https://paper-api.alpaca.markets and verified at runtime, so a live key here
# buys nothing — the paper guard refuses anything else.
ALPACA_API_KEY=your-alpaca-paper-api-key
ALPACA_SECRET_KEY=your-alpaca-paper-secret-key
